===Adjective===
{{en-adj|head=[[color]] [[blind]]}}

# {{context|of a|person or animal|lang=en}} Unable to distinguish between two or more primary colors (usually red and green).
# {{context|of a|person or process|lang=en}} Holding no prejudice based on skin color or [[race]]; not paying attention to skin color.

